{"title":"Bedrock Sandals Release Three New Mountain Clog Color Options","link":"https://theradavist.com/bedrock-sandal-releases-three-new-mountain-clog-color-options/","date":1726009116000,"content":"<p><em>Today Bedrock Sandals releases three new colorways in their Mountain Clog. For those too timid for full-on sandals or those in need of a cozy fall shoe, the Mountain Clog is ideal. </em></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1998\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BedrockSandals_HiRes_110223_BydlonAndrew_L1110986.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BedrockSandals_HiRes_110223_BydlonAndrew_L1110986.jpg?w=1998&amp;quality=75 1998w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BedrockSandals_HiRes_110223_BydlonAndrew_L1110986.jpg?resize=1200,801&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BedrockSandals_HiRes_110223_BydlonAndrew_L1110986.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BedrockSandals_HiRes_110223_BydlonAndrew_L1110986.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Bedrock Mountain Clogs feel like an old friend but surprisingly are still young enough to fly free in the continental US. In less than two years they’ve become a staple for many – typically a piece in their footwear kit they didn’t know they were missing but now can’t live without. They are the cozy campshoe of choice, a sturdy hiker for nearly any trail, and even more surprising, a head turner in the current gorpcore fashion moment.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"887\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BEDROCK_2024_051524_BydlonAndrew_Bedrock100123_BydlonAndrew0764.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BEDROCK_2024_051524_BydlonAndrew_Bedrock100123_BydlonAndrew0764.jpg?w=887&amp;quality=75 887w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BEDROCK_2024_051524_BydlonAndrew_Bedrock100123_BydlonAndrew0764.jpg?resize=768,1154&amp;quality=75 768w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"887\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BEDROCK_2024_051524_BydlonAndrew_Bedrock100123_BydlonAndrew0727.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BEDROCK_2024_051524_BydlonAndrew_Bedrock100123_BydlonAndrew0727.jpg?w=887&amp;quality=75 887w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BEDROCK_2024_051524_BydlonAndrew_Bedrock100123_BydlonAndrew0727.jpg?resize=768,1154&amp;quality=75 768w\" /></p>\n<p>Bedrock Sandals is excited to release 3 new colorways of the Mountain Clog bringing the option count up to seven for diehard Bedrockers and clog curious alike. We’ve added a second nubuck leather option in Driftwood Gray and two new suede leather options in Deep Plum and Ponderosa Brown.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2003\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BEDROCK_2024_051524_BydlonAndrew_Bedrock100123_BydlonAndrew0552.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BEDROCK_2024_051524_BydlonAndrew_Bedrock100123_BydlonAndrew0552.jpg?w=2003&amp;quality=75 2003w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BEDROCK_2024_051524_BydlonAndrew_Bedrock100123_BydlonAndrew0552.jpg?resize=1200,799&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BEDROCK_2024_051524_BydlonAndrew_Bedrock100123_BydlonAndrew0552.jpg?resize=2000,1331&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BEDROCK_2024_051524_BydlonAndrew_Bedrock100123_BydlonAndrew0552.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-BEDROCK_2024_051524_BydlonAndrew_Bedrock100123_BydlonAndrew0552.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Hike up a steep mountain trail and keep those tootsies protected, find rest beside a crackling campfire and be quite cozy, get a shout-out from that one barista, and feel your ego boost tenfold. Whatever your pursuit or pipe dream, Mountain Clogs are equipped to rip in.</p>\n<p>Nubuck Leather Clogs are $175 and Leather Suede Clogs are $160.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2003\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/bedrock-clogs-8.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/bedrock-clogs-8.jpg?w=2003&amp;quality=75 2003w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/bedrock-clogs-8.jpg?resize=1200,799&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/bedrock-clogs-8.jpg?resize=2000,1331&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/bedrock-clogs-8.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/09/bedrock-clogs-8.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em>Check out Spencer’s <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/bedrock-mountain-clog-review/\" target=\"_blank\">long term review</a> if you are clog curious!</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/bedrock-sandal-releases-three-new-mountain-clog-color-options/\">Bedrock Sandals Release Three New Mountain Clog Color Options</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"spencer harding","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"55f426e08805b08ba47535281f9a4cffefd48f54fadd5855c3dbbf8dbf903c20","category":"Cycling"}